celopg.answers.funding_sources: Since 2008, we have secured a total of $224,000 through grant funding and individual donations.   Details: $203,000 from Gitcoin and Giveth, including contributions from Shell and Momus.eth (2020 to present). $17,400 from individual donations through our nonprofit. $3,200 from the Lush Re grant in 2021. $7,000 from Aragon for sponsoring our governance hackathon in 2017. $7,700 from the Threshold Foundation in 2018. .25 ETH ($800) from ENS Small Grants for public goods. This is a small amount of funding compared to the scale and duration of Bloom.
